summary: This is an email chain from August 11, 2019, forwarded within the FBI and OIG, requesting assistance with a crossing inquiry for a person of interest related to the investigation into the death of Jeffrey Epstein on August 10, 2019.

events.title: Death of Jeffrey Epstein
events.description: Jeffrey Epstein died on August 10, 2019, prompting an investigation.

keyFacts: The document is an email chain dated August 11, 2019, concerning the investigation into Jeffrey Epstein's death.
The email requests assistance with a 'crossing inquiry' for a person of interest related to the Epstein case.
Jeffrey Epstein's death occurred on August 10, 2019, as stated in the email.
The correspondence involves multiple agencies, including the FBI and OIG (Office of the Inspector General).
The specific person of interest is not named in the provided text.
